":"2017-01-28T11:48:25.000Z","msg":"ive"},{"pid":"78f16c7f33383cb463fd9b2511345fdfcb8a3fc5","tid":98324,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"《誰人會愛我這種ive仔》<br />\n傳說世間每個人 夠十四分即可得到護蔭<br />\n<br />\n縱使大多彷如弱能 仍得到中六生的身份<br />\n<br />\n可惜像我這一種人 EAA永遠不肯給予憐憫<br />\n<br />\n每天如像乞兒 祈求誰可真心的贈我一分<br />\n<br />\n*<br />\n<br />\n誰成日話我騎呢又柒下 分低到了話我不知羞家<br />\n<br />\n問我物理合格了嗎人被半路撇下<br />\n<br />\n受那風吹雨打<br />\n<br />\n#<br />\n<br />\n誰人會愛我這種IVE仔流落到谷底<br />\n<br />\n恐怕我已是個社會的夢遺<br />\n<br />\n無人前來認領三分低b仔會考再報就等下一世<br />\n<br />\n誰要我這種IVE仔<br />\n<br />\n誰贈我職位<br />\n<br />\n當有美女路過亦不敢發圍<br />\n<br />\n誰在從前話我貧窮但美麗但想抱抱就等待轉世<br />\n<br />\n(唉) 我張cert好貴&quot;"},{"pid":"8b997df1c18e3a5d34dab9228fdd9cabc30b1a6f","tid":98324,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:12:44.000Z","msg":"我有普林斯頓學生證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576ca26345b11255ed885f8789e7c5f4774c919e","tid":98324,"uid":29862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:15:26.000Z","msg":"牛頭角津貼大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051ca8aa6053ab4b41ac906f6c7aae05d7d41304","tid":98324,"uid":34429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:41:52.000Z","msg":"hi found.  dip.  ive仔"},{"pid":"438f3d74b70c8e6301655d70b1105b2703ca2128","tid":98324,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:45:41.000Z","msg":"Ivy League添.<br />\n<br />\n下次可能會話係幫NASA做research."},{"pid":"b1b38898918714418cef6376d50b99373e30acb2","tid":98324,"uid":30469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:45:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13cf1a8e035468d31b111aaa4580693c84176ce1","tid":98324,"uid":62579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquot